<h2>2) Upper: The Slides (Middle Upper Pack)</h2>
<table class='data_table river-stats'>
<tr class='row-1'>
<th>Usual Difficulty</th>
<td>IV-V (for normal flows) </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-2'>
<th>Length</th>
<td>3 Miles </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-3'>
<th>Avg. Gradient</th>
<td>150 fpm</td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-4'>
<th>Max Gradient</th>
<td>250 fpm</td>
</tr>
</table>
